srcinfo.typesrc: 1. City Approval process 2. Service Lists 3. User Feedback 4. Field Checks 5. Departmental requirement for revised area boundaries
srcinfo.srccontr: 1. As the city approves address and street name information it is forwarded to the Maintenance group 2. Water billing lists, Bell Canada service lists are validated against addresses to ensure completeness 3. Feedback from users is fully investigated 4. In disputed cases field checks are conducted. 5. Administrative boundaries are changed on an as-need basis at the instigation of the custodian
